  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e6be890c8a758f3488227c7687955d0c, type: 3}
  m_Name: DashUnlockTaleStone
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::TaleStoneData
  DialogueLines:
  - textVI: "Ng\u1ECDn gi\xF3 c\u1ED5 \u0111\u1EA1i \u0111\xE3 ng\u1EEBng th\u1ED5i
      t\u1EEB l\xE2u... nh\u01B0ng t\xE0n d\u01B0 c\u1EE7a n\xF3 v\u1EABn k\u1EB9t
      l\u1EA1i trong kh\u1ED1i \u0111\xE1 n\xE0y."
    textEN: The ancient breeze fell silent ages ago... but its echoes are still caught
      inside this monolith.
  - textVI: "K\u1EBB b\xE9 nh\u1ECF... h\xE3y mang l\u1EA5y nh\u1ECBp th\u1EDF c\u1EE7a
      ta. V\xE0 x\xE9 to\u1EA1c m\xE0n s\u01B0\u01A1ng."
    textEN: Tiny soul... embrace my breath. And shatter the veil of mist.
